==Keypad== 

The RUST KEYPAD editor combines KED/EDT and Notepad/Wordpad features.
KEYPAD can be used as a typical PDP-11 text editor or as a limited word processor.
Word processor documents are stored in HTML format.

**Warning** KEYPAD is barely in Beta status. See [[Keypad#Limitations|Limitations]]

