**[[#Keypad Word Processing]]Keypad Word Processing**

KEYPAD provides a minimal set of word processing facilities.

• Automatic line-wrapping
• Indents (Gold-E and Gold-D)
• Bullets (Gold-B)
• Horizontal lines (Gold-R)
• Bold font (Ctrl-B)
----
**[[#KEYPAD HTML Subset]]KEYPAD HTML Subset**

KEYPAD supports an HTML subset.

KEYPAD automatically recognises and converts HTML input files. KEYPAD discards all unrecognised HTML objects (and that means most of them). 

You can view, and edit, the HTML rendition with Gold-H. Return to the formatted rendition with Gold-F. 

In the beta you have to manually convert formatted text for HTML storage (with Gold-H).
